{
  "stem": "2833.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she told me that she had no idea when they called her up and told her to come to a certain building in the little town where she lived and take clothes, and I don't know how much and something.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she had no idea that she was going to go to, to a camp and be an SS guard.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So she was nice and she was kind.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She gave us always, especially me, she gave me always a piece of an apple or a piece of bread or something.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, one of the other SS women found out about it and denounced her, and they stripped her and put her in as a prisoner.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And she paid very dearly for being nice and trying to help, which made me very sad.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But there was nothing we could do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And every day, the British were bombing that area.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they threw down leaflets, and they were telling exactly what they're going to bomb.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And it was always at the same hours.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And our factory was on the hill, which was in the middle of that little town.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And on top of that hill was that factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they had bombed constantly around us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And one day they bombed either too early or too late, I don't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But we were still outside the building.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They couldn't lock us in and go to the-- to the cellar.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So we were lined up against the wall of the building as they told us, and they were standing with us.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we-- I looked up like this and I had one of SS girls next to me and she shouted to me, don't look up, they'll see you.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
